COVID-19 vaccination guidelines

At present all employees and students are required to disclose their vaccination status (or submit a valid medical or religious exemption) to the university. All unvaccinated employees, including those with an approved medical or religious exemption, and those who are partially vaccinated, are required to obtain a COVID-19 saliva test on-campus once per 7-day period, 48 or more hours apart with negative test results, and to comply with other mitigation measures.
Please refer to the most recent COVID-19 guidance below:
